<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Calibri, Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 35px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }
    .watermark {
      position: fixed;
      top: 45%;
      left: 15%;
      font-size: 72px;
      color: #f0f0f0;
      transform: rotate(-35deg);
      font-weight: bold;
      z-index: -1;
    }
    .logo-area {
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #003366;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #003366;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .rfp-code {
      background: #003366;
      color: white;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
      gap: 8px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .info-label {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #003366;
    }
    .section {
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .section h3 {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #003366;
      border-left: 5px solid #0066cc;
      padding-left: 10px;
      margin: 15px 0 10px 0;
    }
    ul {
      margin: 8px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    ul li {
      margin: 6px 0;
    }
    .highlight-box {
      background: #e6f2ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
      padding: 12px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .footer-note {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 25px;
      left: 35px;
      right: 35px;
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #888;
      font-style: italic;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="watermark">CONFIDENTIAL</div>
  
  <div class="logo-area">
    {{organisation}}<br>
    Corporate Procurement Division
  </div>

  <h1>Request for Proposal (RFP)</h1>

  <div class="rfp-code">RFP Code: {{tender_id}}</div>

  <div class="info-grid">
    <div class="info-label">RFP Title:</div>
    <div>{{title}}</div>
    
    <div class="info-label">Issue Date:</div>
    <div>{{publish_date}}</div>
    
    <div class="info-label">Proposal Due Date:</div>
    <div>{{due_date}} (5:00 PM Local Time)</div>
    
    <div class="info-label">Project Location:</div>
    <div>{{city}}</div>
    
    <div class="info-label">Budget Estimate:</div>
    <div>INR {{formatCurrency estimated_cost_inr}}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h3>Executive Summary</h3>
    <p>{{organisation}} is seeking qualified vendors to submit proposals for the supply and delivery of <strong>{{material}}</strong> for our {{city}} facility. This procurement is part of our infrastructure modernization initiative.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    <strong>Material Category:</strong> {{product_category}}<br>
    <strong>Delivery Timeline:</strong> 8-10 weeks from PO issuance<br>
    <strong>Inspection Requirements:</strong> Third-party inspection at manufacturer's works
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h3>Scope of Supply</h3>
    <p>The selected vendor shall provide:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Supply of {{material}} conforming to latest IS/IEC standards</li>
      <li>Factory acceptance testing (FAT) with third-party witness</li>
      <li>Packaging suitable for long-distance transportation</li>
      <li>Delivery to {{city}} location with unloading assistance</li>
      <li>Comprehensive warranty coverage for 24 months</li>
      <li>Technical documentation and test certificates</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h3>Technical Requirements</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Material Specification:</strong> {{material}}</li>
      <li><strong>Conductor:</strong> Electrolytic grade copper (EC Grade), Class 2 stranded as per IS 8130</li>
      <li><strong>Insulation Type:</strong> XLPE (Cross-linked Polyethylene), thermosetting compound</li>
      <li><strong>Voltage Class:</strong> 1.1 kV / 11 kV grade (as applicable)</li>
      <li><strong>Standards:</strong> IS 7098 Part 1 & 2, IEC 60502-1, BIS certification mandatory</li>
      <li><strong>Testing:</strong> Routine and type test reports from NABL labs required</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h3>Vendor Qualification Criteria</h3>
    <p>To be eligible, vendors must demonstrate:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Minimum 3 years of experience in manufacturing similar products</li>
      <li>At least THREE reference orders from utilities/industrial clients (value &gt; ₹5 Cr each)</li>
      <li>Manufacturing capacity: Minimum 300 MT per month</li>
      <li>Quality certifications: ISO 9001:2015 (mandatory), ISO 14001 (preferred)</li>
      <li>Financial soundness: Average turnover ≥ ₹25 Crores in last 3 years</li>
      <li>Technical capability: In-house testing laboratory with calibrated equipment</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h3>Commercial Terms</h3>
    <div class="info-grid">
      <div class="info-label">Price Basis:</div>
      <div>Firm, non-escalable for 180 days</div>
      
      <div class="info-label">Payment Terms:</div>
      <div>70% against dispatch, 20% after receipt & inspection, 10% after 90 days</div>
      
      <div class="info-label">Security Deposit:</div>
      <div>3% of order value (as bank guarantee)</div>
      
      <div class="info-label">Liquidated Damages:</div>
      <div>0.5% per week of delay, max 10% of order value</div>
      
      <div class="info-label">Warranty Period:</div>
      <div>24 months from commissioning or 30 months from supply, whichever is earlier</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h3>Contact for Clarifications</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Name:</strong> {{contact_person}}<br>
      <strong>Designation:</strong> General Manager - Procurement<br>
      <strong>Email:</strong> {{contact_email}}<br>
      <strong>Phone:</strong> {{contact_phone}}<br>
      <strong>Office Address:</strong> {{organisation}}, {{city}}
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-note">
    Confidential Document | RFP {{tender_id}} | Authorized vendors only | Auto-generated for demonstration purposes
  </div>
</body>
</html>